summary: This is a property deed (indenture) recorded in New York City, transferring ownership of a plot of land in Manhattan. The document references a prior deed from 'Hurley, Ltd.' dated July 23, 1997, and is formally recorded on October 11, 2000.

events.title: Prior Deed from Hurley, Ltd.
events.description: A deed transferring the property to the grantor of the current document was executed by Hurley, Ltd.

events.title: Recording of Property Deed
events.description: The current indenture (deed) is officially recorded in the Office of the City Register of New York City.

locations: County and State of New York
keyFacts: This is a legal property deed (indenture) for a plot of land in Manhattan, New York City.
The deed was officially recorded on October 11, 2000.
The property was previously conveyed to the current grantor by a deed from 'Hurley, Ltd.' dated July 23, 1997, and recorded on November 17, 1997.
The document contains standard legal boilerplate for property conveyance, including clauses about taxes and improvements.
No individuals are explicitly named in the provided text; the parties are referred to generically as 'grantor' and 'grantee'.
